<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		{% block stylesheets %}
			{{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
		{% endblock %}
	</head>
	<body class="antialiased text-slate-400 bg-gradient-to-tr from-bg-blue-950 from-50% to-slate-700">
		{% block body %}
			<div class="mx-auto min-h-screen max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-12 font-sans md:px-12 md:py-20 lg:px-24 lg:py-0">
				<div class="lg:flex lg:justify-between lg:gap-4">
					<header class="lg:sticky lg:top-0 lg:flex lg:max-h-screen lg:w-1/2 lg:flex-col lg:justify-between lg:py-24">
						<div>
              <div class="flex justify-between gap-2 flex-row">
                <div class="basis-1/4"><img class="rounded-2xl max-h-24"  src="{{ asset('images/moi.jpeg') }}"></div>
                <div class="basis-3/4">
                  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-5x">Clément BOUDINEL</h1>
							    <h2 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-xl">Développeur Back-End chez Lesgrappes</h2>
                </div>
              </div>
							<p class="mt-4 leading-normal">J'assure la maintenance et l'évolution de la platforme.</p>
							<nav class="nav hidden lg:block" aria-label="In-page jump links">
								<ul class="mt-16 w-max">
									<li>
										<a class="group flex items-center py-3 active" href="#about">
											<span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-slate-600 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-amber-500 group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-amber-500 motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
											<span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 group-hover:text-amber-500 group-focus-visible:text-amber-500">À propos</span>
										</a>
									</li>
									<li>
										<a class="group flex items-center py-3" href="#experience">
											<span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-slate-600 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-amber-500 group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-amber-500 motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
											<span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 group-hover:text-amber-500 group-focus-visible:text-amber-500">Expérience</span>
										</a>
									</li>
									<li>
										<a class="group flex items-center py-3" href="#projects">
											<span class="nav-indicator mr-4 h-px w-8 bg-slate-600 transition-all group-hover:w-16 group-hover:bg-amber-500 group-focus-visible:w-16 group-focus-visible:bg-amber-500 motion-reduce:transition-none"></span>
											<span class="nav-text text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 group-hover:text-amber-500 group-focus-visible:text-amber-500">Projets</span>
										</a>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</nav>
						</div>
					</header>
					<main class="pt-24 lg:w-1/2 lg:py-24">
						<section id="about" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24" aria-label="About me">
							<div class="sticky top-0 z-20 -mx-6 mb-4 w-screen bg-slate-900/75 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur md:-mx-12 md:px-12 lg:sr-only lg:relative lg:top-auto lg:mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-0 lg:py-0 lg:opacity-0">
								<h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-200 lg:sr-only">À propos</h2>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="mb-4">
									Il y a maintenant plus de 10 ans, j'entrais en fac de médecine ou ... j'ai commencé à développer mes premiers programmes.<br>
									Un ans plus tard, j'entamais un cursus de 5 ans jusqu'a l'obtention de mon
									<a class="text-amber-500">Mastère en Ingénierie du Web</a>.
								</p>
								<p class="mb-4">
									D'abord intéressé par le développement de logiciels, je me suis rapidement réorienter vers le
									<a class="text-amber-500">Développement Web</a>
									ainsi que la
									<a class="text-amber-500">Gestion de projet</a>.
								</p>
								<p class="mb-4">
									Je contribue aujourd'hui avec mon équipe à l'évolution du site développer en
									<a class="text-amber-500">PHP</a>
									avec l'utilisation du
									<a class="text-amber-500">CMS Magento</a>
									mais également au developpement d'une
									<a class="text-amber-500">API</a>
									sous le framework
									<a class="text-amber-500">Phalcon PHP</a>.
								</p>
								<p class="mb-4">
									<a class="text-amber-500">Mes principaux objectifs</a>
									ces jours-ci sont de me former à la suite
									<a class="text-amber-500">ELK</a>
									(Elasticsearch, Logstash et Kibana) et monter en compétence sur le framework
									<a class="text-amber-500">Symfony</a>.
								</p>
							</div>
						</section>
						<section id="experience" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24">
							<div class="sticky top-0 z-20 -mx-6 mb-4 w-screen bg-slate-900/75 px-6 py-5 backdrop-blur md:-mx-12 md:px-12 lg:sr-only lg:relative lg:top-auto lg:mx-auto lg:w-full lg:px-0 lg:py-0 lg:opacity-0">
								<h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-200 lg:sr-only">Expérience</h2>
							</div>
						</section>
					</main>
				</div>
			</div>
		{% endblock %}
	</body>
</html>
